l up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.07"},{"pid":"e63d246bf63ea04f0dec35bc95f7c796022a39cf","tid":1548053,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4dac7fc17af0518dce092f198b9e352e5b2b357","tid":1548053,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"世界警察"},{"pid":"b595b97339a0bf76bae9d32fa2db7541a00654f6","tid":1548053,"uid":162731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a00b20e7650bc9c16413fd63871aeda97e6072d","tid":1548053,"uid":292246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73df88004e2ff75289451f26d2a1900f2a3dd40f","tid":1548053,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:51:41.000Z","msg":"Chancellor Merkel, since you&rsquo;ve decided to go ahead with your trip to Beijing, want to make sure you&rsquo;ve seen this video&hellip; @GermanAmbUSA @HeikoMaas 1/4<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iejjwdxQDYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiejjwdxQDYw&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=2f0ebfbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iejjwdxQDYw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e087308f003b8f3f46ef59866d8142cfb4cd0b1f","tid":1548053,"uid":181789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"上啊 香港人"},{"pid":"d449b8b1f52e91481af91c7d0ac44429a547ef8f","tid":1548053,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"